page.title: 17Wild life.Birds
page.content: Canal or River - Water hen,mallard, grey wagtail,swallow,swan,heron, kingfisher.Canada geese on the former gravel pit. Gardens-house sparrow,hedge sparrow, chaffinch,goldfinch,greenfinch, bullfinch,starling,pied wagtail, robin,blackbird,song thrush,blue tit, great tit, coal tit,treecreeper,wren, house martin,swallow, swift,ring dove wood pigeon,black-headed gull,herring gull. Pasture and moorland-magpie,curlew, skylark,crow,cuckoo,snipe,ring plover, lapwing,pheasant,kestrel and sparrow hawk.
